'''Necropolis''' was a slang term used to refer to [[Coruscant/Legends|Yuuzhan'tar]], the [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongformed]] Coruscant, by those [[Coruscanti/Legends|Coruscanti]] and resistance fighters who stayed behind and fought.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

